title: Hour 2 - The Tua Rule, Nebraska's Embarrassing Win
itunes:title: Hour 2 - The Tua Rule, Nebraska's Embarrassing Win
description:
Dan addresses the changes in the roughing the passer penalty calls after Miami Dolphins QB Tua Togovailoa's recent head injuries. And he lambastes Nebraska for their over-energetic celebration after beating a middling Rutgers squad.
